item.title: CiberNetics
item.author: Phalerovia
item.description: CiberNetics is a competition designed to introduce beginners to Red VS Blue Team competitions. In this competition team of two people will compete with each other with the goal of gathering all the flags in the other team’s server, while protecting their own flag.
